Open Source platformer game for GNU/Linux, PC/Window$ and OUYA/Android game console.
This software licensed under the terms of BSD-2 (read COPYING for details).


Building:

It builds on Gentoo GNU/Linux (x86_64) with:
    =sys-devel/gcc-4.5.4
    =dev-util/cmake-2.8.6-r4
    =sys-devel/make-3.82-r1
    =media-libs/freeglut-2.8.0
    =x11-apps/mesa-progs-8.0.1
    =dev-lang/python-2.7.2-r3
    =dev-python/imaging-1.1.7 (PIL)

In future will be also used:
    =dev-java/sun-jdk-1.6.0.33 (jdk-6u33-linux-x64.bin) (http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk6-downloads-1637591.html)
    =dev-util/android-ndk-8b
    =dev-util/android-sdk-update-manager-20.0.3 with Android 4.0.3 (API 15)

Other dependencies (already in repo):
    pugixml-1.2 (MIT license)
    sigslot (Public domain) http://sigslot.sourceforge.net/ https://gitorious.org/sigslot
    TGA loader (?) http://www.dreamincode.net/code/snippet2076.htm
    AtlasGenerator (MIT license) https://github.com/pjohalloran/texture-atlas-generator/blob/master/AtlasGenerator.py
